<subSubSection id="C33C09E7FFEBFFB267206F79FAB9BE7D" pageId="0" pageNumber="103" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B995A6CFFEBFFB267206F79FAB9BE7D" blockId="0.[831,1437,1605,1820]" pageId="0" pageNumber="103">
<emphasis id="B952867EFFEBFFB267206F79FC03BF3D" bold="true" box="[831,945,1605,1628]" pageId="0" pageNumber="103">Remarks:</emphasis>
Seven species of 
<taxonomicName id="4C2621EFFFEBFFB2608B6F79FB49BF3D" authorityName="Erichson" authorityYear="1845" box="[1172,1275,1605,1628]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Baeocera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="103" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B952867EFFEBFFB2608B6F79FB49BF3D" box="[1172,1275,1605,1628]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="103">Baeocera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are currently known from the 
<collectingCountry id="F3311AFCFFEBFFB260136F59FBC7BF1D" box="[1036,1141,1637,1660]" name="Indonesia" pageId="0" pageNumber="103">Moluccas</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFB7279DFFEBFFB260946F59FAA9BF1D" author="Lobl I." box="[1163,1307,1637,1660]" pageId="0" pageNumber="103" pagination="165 - 187" refId="ref11281" refString="Lobl I. 2015 a. Contribution to the knowledge of the Scaphidiinae (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae) of the Moluccas. Stuttgarter Beitrage zur Naturkunde A, Neue Serie 8: 165 - 187." type="journal article" year="2015">Löbl, 2015a</bibRefCitation>
), while 12 have been reported from the Lesser Sunda, and 18 from New 
<collectingCountry id="F3311AFCFFEBFFB267666F99FC74BFDD" box="[889,966,1701,1724]" name="Guinea-Bissau" pageId="0" pageNumber="103">Guinea</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFB7279DFFEBFFB267C96F99FBFDBFDD" author="Lobl I." box="[982,1103,1701,1724]" pageId="0" pageNumber="103" pagination="1 - 20" refId="ref11223" refString="Lobl I. 2002. On Baeocera (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Scaphidiinae) of New Guinea. Mitteilungen der Schweizerischen entomologischen Gesellschaft 75: 1 - 20." type="journal article" year="2002">Löbl, 2002</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFB7279DFFEBFFB260446F99FB10BFDD" author="Lobl I." box="[1115,1186,1701,1724]" pageId="0" pageNumber="103" pagination="65 - 120" refId="ref11317" refString="Lobl I. 2015 b. On the Scaphidiinae (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae) of the Lesser Sunda Island. Revue suisse de Zoologie 122: 65 - 120." type="journal article" year="2015">2015b</bibRefCitation>
). Most of these species are members of the monophyletic 
<taxonomicName id="4C2621EFFFEBFFB260DD6FF9FAABBFBD" baseAuthorityName="Lobl" baseAuthorityYear="1971" box="[1218,1305,1732,1756]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Baeocera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="103" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lenta">
<emphasis id="B952867EFFEBFFB260DD6FF9FAABBFBD" box="[1218,1305,1732,1756]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="103">B. lenta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group. The present collection comprises six additional Moluccan species, all but one members of that group.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
